OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FAbuse survivors hear       
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FStormont public apology    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Survivors of historical institutional  
OL,6, abuse in Northern Ireland have been    
OL,7, told that the state believes them - and
OL,8, is sorry.                              
OL,10,FMinisters from the five main Stormont  
OL,11,Fparties made statements of apology in  
OL,12,Fthe Northern Ireland Assembly.         
OL,14,FIt follows a 2017 inquiry which        
OL,15,Fexamined the abuse of hundreds of      
OL,16,Fchildren at Church and state-run       
OL,17,Finstitutions over seven decades.       
OL,19,FThe move was welcomed by some; others  
OL,20,Fsaid it was too little, too late.      
